  "name": "Building Blocks - FiniteDifferenceMethod4PDES \u2014 OGC Building Block Register",
  "abstract": "OGC Building Block register for all ODE/PDE models implemented in FiniteDifferenceMethod4PDES (Java/Maven, MVC architecture). Covers 22 local kinetic models across 4 complexity tiers, 4 Holling functional response components, and 2 spatial operators, all described using SOSA, PROV-O and STAC 1.0.\n",
  "modified": "2026-05-20T15:11:38.640400",
  "tooling": {
    "bblocks-postprocess": {
      "commitId": "\"1c38e230d79a22d5b242ea63ec3c6d6a95af173d",
      "shortCommitId": "\"1c38e2",
      "date": "2026-05-20T11:46:31+00:00\""
    }
  },
